<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{% block title %}職能發展學院{% endblock %}  </title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{url_for('static', filename='css/base.css')}}">
</head>
<body>
    <header class="site-header">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="logo">
                <a href="#">職能發展學院</a>
            </div>
            <nav class="main-navigation">
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="{{url_for('index')}}">Home</a></li>
                    <li><a href="{{url_for('classes')}}">課程規劃</a></li>
                    <li><a href="{{url_for('news')}}">最新消息</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#">交通資訊</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#">聯絡我們</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
            <button class="menu-toggle" aria-controls="primary-menu" aria-expanded="false">
                menu
            </button>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <div class="container">
        {% block main %}
            <h1>歡迎來到職能發展學院</h1>
            <p>這是一個符合 RWD 的基礎網頁框架，您可以基於此框架繼續開發您的網站內容。</p>
            <p>此框架的導覽列是根據您提供的圖片設計的。</p>
            {% endblock %}
        </div>
    </main>

<footer>
        <div class="footer-container">
            <div class="footer-top">
                <div class="footer-logo">
                    <img src="{{url_for('static', filename='images/justHomeLogo.png')}}" alt="JustHome Logo" class="logo-img">
                    <span class="logo-text"></span> 
                    
                </div>
                <nav class="footer-nav">
                    <ul>
                        <li><a href="#">Discover</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#">Quick Link</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#">Contact Us</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#">Our Address</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#">Get App</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </nav>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-bottom">
                <p>&copy; <span id="currentYear"></span> 職能發展學院. 版權所有.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="{{url_for('static', filename='js/index.js')}}"></script>
</body>
</html>